.TH "set_link_hw_format" 9 "set_link_hw_format" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
set_link_hw_format \- Set the HW audio format of the physical DAI link.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" set_link_hw_format
.BI "(struct snd_soc_dai_link *link "  ","
.BI "struct snd_soc_tplg_link_config *cfg "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "link" 12
\fIsnd_soc_dai_link\fP which should be updated
.IP "cfg" 12
physical link configs.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Topology context contains a list of supported HW formats (configs) and
a default format ID for the physical link. This function will use this
default ID to choose the HW format to set the link's DAI format for init.
